-- Sasol Agrees With Waertsilae to Operate South Africa Gas Project
-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 2012-05-13T10:49:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-13/sasol-agrees-with-waertsilae-to-operate-south-africa-gas-project.html
Waertsilae Oyj (WRT1V) , the world’s biggest
maker of ship motors and power plants, will operate and maintain
 Sasol Ltd.’s (SOL)  gas power plant in Sasolburg, South Africa, Sasaol
said in an e-mailed statement today.  The plant will produce more than 140 megawatts from 2013,
Sasol said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
